        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Spaces, equipment and physical structures that are available for practising different sports and recreational activities in a sports centre.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="es">instalaciones del polideportivo</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">sports centre premises</rdfs:label>
